Sentencas: Here we report solid oxide cells with thin strontium- and magnesium-doped lanthanum gallate electrolytes that yield power densities of 1.06 W cm(-2) at 550 degrees C and 0.81 W cm(-2) at 500 degrees C when operated on humidified hydrogen and ambient air.
Titulo: A solid oxide cell yielding high power density below 600 °C

Sentencas: Cost-effective ceramic processing and chemical solution impregnation methods were utilized, yielding a dual micron- and nano-scale architecture that is essential for achieving good low-temperature performance.
Titulo: A solid oxide cell yielding high power density below 600 °C
